Package: maplegend
Title: Legends for Maps
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person("TimothÃ©e", "Giraud", email = "timothee.giraud@cnrs.fr",
    role = c("cre","aut"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-1932-3323")))
Description: Create legends for maps or other graphics. Maps with a full layout
    need to have legends on it. Proportional symbols, typologies, choropleth,
    line maps, all these maps needs legends to be read. It is possible to
    combine several legends in a single block.
